	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Tarelan<br />
<br />
From what I understand you need to use /hitsmode my on, /hitsmode me on, /hitsmode others on<br />
<br />
By using /hitsmode off you turn all hit messages off.  Using m2,m3 etc puts the messages in the windows, the on setting puts them back to where they were.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
