	Location: The Hunter's Lodge
</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Here's my current setup:<br />
<br />
------------------------------------------------------------<br />
/hitsmode my m3 100 598 5 1 1 1 220 1<br />
<br />
EQCLIENT.INI settings:<br />
<br />
MyHitsMode=3<br />
MyHitsX=100<br />
MyHitsY=598<br />
MyHitsCount=5<br />
MyHitsFontSize=1<br />
MyHitsShowHeader=1<br />
MyHitsShowBG=1<br />
MyHitsBGWidth=220<br />
<br />
------------------------------------------------------------<br />
/hitsmode me m3 323 598 5 1 1 1 220 1<br />
<br />
EQCLIENT.INI settings:<br />
<br />
OtherHitsMeMode=3<br />
OtherHitsMeX=323<br />
OtherHitsMeY=598<br />
OtherHitsMeCount=5<br />
OtherHitsMeFontSize=1<br />
OtherHitsMeShowHeader=1<br />
OtherHitsMeShowBG=1<br />
OtherHitsMeBGWidth=220<br />
<br />
------------------------------------------------------------<br />
/hitsmode other m3 546 598 5 1 1 1 220 1<br />
<br />
EQCLIENT.INI settings:<br />
<br />
OtherHitsOtherMode=3<br />
OtherHitsOtherX=546<br />
OtherHitsOtherY=598<br />
OtherHitsOtherCount=5<br />
OtherHitsOtherFontSize=1<br />
OtherHitsOtherShowHeader=1<br />
OtherHitsOtherShowBG=1<br />
OtherHitsOtherBGWidth=220<br />
MyHitsAlwaysDraw=1<br />
OtherHitsMeAlwaysDraw=1<br />
OtherHitsOtherAlwaysDraw=1<br />
<br />
<br />
<img src="http://users2.ev1.net/~ej_james/everquest/misc/hitsmode.jpg" border="0" alt=""><br />
<br />
Actually, I've moved my character info box over a bit and extended my "OtherHitsOtherBGWidth" to 250 to accomodate for some of the longer player and mob names being displayed in that window.</p>
	
	
	
